ChangeNote:
Change on this defect fix an issue when in Asset Manager  for TBA instrument type value for maturity date/maturity price  key ratios were different than in PFC. Before, Maturity date in AM shows values from static data. After code change, Maturity date value comes from  calculation result which is identical behavior to what we have in PFC. Maturity price for 'external calculation' price method now is identical in Asset manager and PFC and is calculated:
a) when maturity price is provided by external source then we keep maturity price from the external source;
b) when maturity price is NOT provided by external source then we calculate maturity price based on OffBalance position.
